Package: tool-x
Version: 2.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pip, git
Maintainer: Mentat <mentat@example.com>
Description: Tool-X - Kali Linux Hacking Tools Installer
 Tool-X is a Kali Linux hacking tools installer that allows
 users to install approximately 370+ hacking tools for 
 Termux and Linux systems. Tool-X simplifies the process of 
 installing and managing various security tools used for 
 penetration testing and security research.
